 <div style={{ background: "var(--amber-b)", border: "1px solid var(--amber)", borderRadius: 6, padding: "8px 12px", fontSize: 12, color: "var(--amber-l)", }}>
                ⚠ Prevailing wage rates apply to all labor on this project per applicable statutes.
              </div>
