// ============================================================
// GROUNDWORK — CUSTOMER PORTAL v1.0
//
// Client-facing web portal (light theme — distinct from internal UI)
// Two account types share the same portal with contextual UX:
//
//   RESIDENTIAL customers see:
//     - Open & past service requests
//     - Technician ETA + live job status
//     - Estimate approval with digital signature
//     - Invoice view + online payment
//     - Service agreement status + renewal
//     - Equipment on file
//     - Request new service (lead → CRM)
//
//   COMMERCIAL accounts see all of the above, plus:
//     - Multi-project dashboard across all active jobs
//     - Certified payroll & compliance docs
//     - Submittal / RFI / O&M document library
//     - Purchase order + change order tracking
//     - Multi-contact account management
//
// Production integration points:
//   - Auth: JWT token issued on login, scoped to contactId
//   - Data: REST API reads from same DB as internal modules
//   - Payments: Stripe embedded checkout (amount + invoice ref)
//   - Signatures: DocuSign or SignNow embedded iframe
//   - File uploads: S3 presigned URL
//   - Real-time ETA: Dispatch module GPS → push notification
// ============================================================

